Published on Sep 4, 2014This program is the fifth in the series of The Leon Charney Reports on the Israeli-Palestinian situation with Hasan Abdel Rahman, Micha Paz, Ghaith Al-Omari, Ehud Barak, Ehud Olmert, Arye Naor and Hussein Ibish on The Leon Charney Report. It originally featured an interview with Hasan Abdel Rahman and Micha Paz on the Israeli-Palestinian Peace Process. However, it has been updated with interviews from Ghaith al-Omari, Ehud Barak, Ehud Olmert, Arey Naor and Hussein Ibish conducted in the Summer of 2013.  Read more about Hasan Abdel Rahman: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hassan_A...Read more about Ghaith al-Omari: http://www.americantaskforce.org/staf...Read more about Ehud Barak: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ehud_BarakRead more about Ehud Olmert: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ehud_OlmertRead more about Hussein Ibish: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hussein_... Broadcast Date: August 10 & April 27, 2014With interviews from March 5, 1995 http://charneyreport.com/ Like Leon Charney on Facebookhttps://www.facebook.com/LeonCharney Follow Leon Charney on Twitterhttps://twitter.com/#!/leoncharney 



