»



 Ehud Barak






Ehud Barak was born on February 12, 1942 in Kibbutz Mishmar Ha-Sharon, Palestine as Ehud Brug. He was previously married to Na'ava Barak.            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

February 12, 
     
1942

            in
            Kibbutz Mishmar Ha-Sharon, Palestine [now Israel]










 


